abstract: Soccer coaches Robbie Deans of Australia and Graham Henry of New Zealand have been eager to downplay their rivalry in buildup to their Rugby World Cup semifinal, but it is clear that defeat to the other would be an unpalatable experience.
snippet: The Australia and New Zealand coaches have been eager to downplay their rivalry in the buildup to the match, but it is clear that defeat to the other would be an unpalatable experience.
